                    "body": "Here we are looking at microperformance of 250 nanoseconds versus 1200 nanoseconds. I do not believe this code path has been optimized for nanosecond-level microperformance. If this is important to you, you are free to investigate and propose improvements (and add some benchmarks to our ASV suite so we can keep an eye on this). ",
